                            <comment id="13757272" author="stack" created="Wed, 4 Sep 2013 00:01:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Does this work because you have moved the splitting after other DFS ops so it will stall there until out of safe mode?  If so +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13757297" author="jxiang" created="Wed, 4 Sep 2013 00:27:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, that&apos;s right. The splitting is moved after the root folder check, version checking, etc. So it won&apos;t start to work on failed splitting tasks when a cluster restarts and hdfs hasn&apos;t moved out of safe mode yet.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
